summary:
If Not For You, Bran IV Summary:  

The many armies are gathering in the North to fight the Others. Meanwhile there are people...
body:
If Not For You, Bran IV

Summary: 

The many armies are gathering in the North to fight the Others. Meanwhile there are people with grievances to be addressed, old friends and old enemies to be reunited, new meetings, information to be revealed, and old wounds to be healed.

Chapter Summary: 

The war is over but there are still matters to attend to

Bran IV | Read from beginning

for @theladyofhouseslytherin

There was a time jump between the last couple chapters and this chapter. As I’ve said before I don’t really care to detail the endgame and I don’t want to write any more fight sequences.

This is the second-to-last chapter btw. I’ll post the final one next Sunday after I get back from my vacation.

summary: The Echoes of Stories Never Told
title: The Echoes of Stories Never Told
body:
Author: copperbadge

Fandom: Game Of Thrones

Rating: Teen

Words: 6,011

Summary: Gendry looks out for all the kids who come to his foster home, but Arya is different right from the start.

Link: https://archiveofourown.org/works/2283096

Review: This was less about them being in a foster home together, and more about their relationship which started in a foster home. I really liked the development, the dedication they showed to each other, and how to story moved with them from the foster home.
